# ORIG TITLE    Right wing, right here, right now . 
# ORIG CONTENT  Is a new form of right-wing politics sweeping Europe? . Beyond terrorist attacks and lone wolves like Norway’s Anders Bering Brevik, support for extreme political parties is on the rise. In Greece the openly neo-Nazi Golden Dawn party now polls more than 10 percent. But it is not only Europe’s debt stricken countries that are witnessing a wave in far-right support. Countries which were once seen as open and tolerant are also seeing a shift. 
